commentary: Jones to Misbah-ul-Haq, FOUR runs there it is the winning runs come from the bat of Misbah-ul-Haq which is quite fitting seeing it is his birthday today. Jones strays to far onto leg stump and as Ireland had brought all the fielders up close there was no fielder on the leg boundary.
